## Resolved Design Decisions

> [!NOTE]
> **Q1: Streak timezone — RESOLVED → Asia/Dhaka (UTC+6).**
> The streak "day boundary" uses `Asia/Dhaka` timezone, matching the user base. The `update_streak` RPC will compute `(now() AT TIME ZONE 'Asia/Dhaka')::date` instead of `CURRENT_DATE`.

> [!NOTE]
> **Q2: Daily goal default — RESOLVED → 0 (prompt to set).**
> New users see `daily_goal_minutes = 0`, which triggers a "Set your daily goal" prompt in the UI. No implicit default.

> [!NOTE]
> **Q3: To-Do persistence — RESOLVED → Both options.**
> To-do items persist until manually completed/deleted. Additionally, an `auto_reset_daily` boolean flag on each item allows users to mark items as "recurring daily" — these auto-uncheck at day boundary (Dhaka time). Default is `false` (persistent).

